<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 06:20:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国比亚迪在第三季度增长中提高产量和招聘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-boosts-production-hiring-amid-q3-growth-2024-11-03/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪执行副总裁何志奇周六在微博上表示，从8月到10月，比亚迪产量增加了近20万辆，同时在汽车制造和零部件领域雇佣了近20万名新员工。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 04:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-boosts-production-hiring-amid-q3-growth-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>2024年前9个月中国结婚登记量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriage-registrations-china-drop-first-nine-months-2024-2024-11-03/</link><description>民政部的官方数据显示，中国已经出台了一系列措施来提振不断下降的人口水平，但 2024 年前 9 个月的结婚登记人数有所下降。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 03:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/marriage-registrations-china-drop-first-nine-months-2024-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国国务院总理李强将在上海进口博览会上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-premier-li-qiang-speak-import-expo-shanghai-2024-11-03/</link><description>中国商务部周日表示，中国总理李强将在本周的中国国际进口博览会开幕式上发表讲话，北京方面试图表明步履蹒跚的经济是开放的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 03:51:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-premier-li-qiang-speak-import-expo-shanghai-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>科里卡希望在新来的奥克兰队保持澳超联赛的完美开局后保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/corica-wants-consistency-after-newcomers-auckland-maintain-perfect-a-league-2024-11-03/</link><description>周六，奥克兰足球俱乐部主教练史蒂夫·科里卡带领球队以2-0战胜惠灵顿凤凰队，这是俱乐部在首个赛季中取得的三连胜，他希望这支A联赛的新人能够专注于保持他们令人印象深刻的赛季初状态。</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Nov 2024 03:05:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/corica-wants-consistency-after-newcomers-auckland-maintain-perfect-a-league-2024-11-03/</guid></item><item><title>格罗方德因向受制裁的中国公司运送芯片而被美国罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五表示，对总部位于纽约的全球第三大代工芯片制造商 GlobalFoundries 处以 50 万美元的罚款，原因是其未经授权向被列入黑名单的中国芯片制造商中芯国际的一家子公司运送芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 18:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-penalizes-globalfoundries-shipping-chips-chinese-firm-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国将免签政策扩大到韩国等9个国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国将向韩国、挪威和芬兰等另外九个国家的公民提供免签入境政策。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 13:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-visa-free-policy-9-more-countries-including-south-korea-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国确认欧盟代表团访问电动汽车关税谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国商务部周五证实，欧盟将派代表来华就电动汽车关税争端中的价格承诺进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-confirms-eu-delegation-visit-ev-tariff-talks-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使在俄中北极军事合作中看到一些“令人担忧的信号”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-sees-some-concerning-signals-russia-china-military-cooperation-arctic-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国北极大使表示，美国正在密切关注俄罗斯和中国在北极地区日益增长的合作，两国最近在该地区的一些军事合作发出了“令人担忧的信号”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 12:26:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-envoy-sees-some-concerning-signals-russia-china-military-cooperation-arctic-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国与斯洛伐克在欧盟贸易争端中建立更紧密的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-underscores-benefits-cooperation-with-slovakia-during-ficos-visit-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国和斯洛伐克周五表示，他们将加强贸易和投资关系，并在罗伯特·菲科总理访问北京以建立新的战略伙伴关系期间谈到了乌克兰和平的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 11:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-underscores-benefits-cooperation-with-slovakia-during-ficos-visit-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，中国希望美国无论谁赢得大选，都将继续在气候变化问题上合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</link><description>一位政府高级官员周五表示，无论下周总统选举结果如何，中国希望美国能够继续在气候变化问题上与其他国家合作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 10:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-hopes-us-will-continue-climate-change-collaboration-whoever-wins-election-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>受制裁打击的中国科技行业对特朗普和哈里斯总统任期的影响感到困惑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普下周赢得美国总统职位将比卡马拉·哈里斯获胜更让中国科技公司的前景变得混乱，高管们表示，他不可预测的风格可能会像增加限制一样让受到制裁打击的行业得到缓和。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 08:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-sanction-hit-tech-industry-puzzles-over-impact-trump-harris-presidencies-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国转向美国农产品进口有助于抵御贸易战风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</link><description>中国自2018年以来努力改变粮食进口来源，这使得如果美国总统大选后中美贸易摩擦爆发，中国更有能力对美国农产品征收针锋相对的关税，同时减少对中国粮食安全的损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-pivot-us-farm-imports-bolsters-it-against-trade-war-risks-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责对中国著名人权捍卫者的判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</link><description>美国周五谴责中国著名人权律师余文生及其妻子徐艳的“不公正监禁”，中国一家法院本周分别判处他们三年和一年零九个月的刑期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 03:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-condemns-sentencing-prominent-chinese-human-rights-defenders-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国研究人员在梅塔骆驼背上开发军事用途人工智能模型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</link><description>根据三篇学术论文和分析师的说法，与中国人民解放军有联系的中国顶级研究机构已使用 Meta 公开的 Llama 模型来开发一种用于潜在军事应用的人工智能工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-researchers-develop-ai-model-military-use-back-metas-llama-2024-11-01/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”残骸掠过中国海岸后，台湾进行了清理工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</link><description>周五，强大的台风“康瑞”席卷台湾，造成两人死亡，交通运输中断，风暴余波掠过中国海岸后，台湾天气晴朗，办公楼和金融市场重新开放。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 02:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/taiwan-clears-up-remnant-typhoon-kong-rey-brushes-chinese-coast-2024-11-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>